# Shellkode HR Scheduler — Use Case Definition

---

## Problem Statement

Enterprise employee onboarding is a **fragmented, manual, multi-stakeholder process** spanning recruiters, HR teams, and new hires — each using disconnected tools (email, spreadsheets, shared drives). This leads to slow offer cycles, missed onboarding steps, poor Day-1 experiences, and zero pipeline visibility across teams.

---

## Solution

An **AI-powered, end-to-end hiring and onboarding platform** with three role-based portals that automate the entire journey — from candidate selection to a fully onboarded, productive employee.

---

## The Three Portals

### 1. 🎯 Recruiter Portal

**Purpose**: Manage the offer letter pipeline from selection to acceptance.

| Capability | Description |
|---|---|
| Candidate Pipeline Dashboard | Track candidates across stages — Selected, Offer Sent, Negotiating, Accepted, Rejected |
| AI Offer Letter Generation | LLM generates personalized offer letters from candidate profile, role, and recruiter notes |
| One-Click Offer Dispatch | Review, edit, attach documents, and send offers directly from the portal |
| LLM Reply Classification | AI auto-classifies candidate email replies as Accept / Negotiate / Reject / Needs Review |
| Smart Counter-Responses | AI drafts negotiation responses for recruiter approval |
| Seamless HR Handoff | Convert accepted candidates to New Hires with one click — data flows into HR portal |

---

### 2. 🏢 HR Portal

**Purpose**: Orchestrate the full onboarding journey for new hires handed off by recruiters.

| Capability | Description |
|---|---|
| Onboarding Dashboard | Pipeline stats — Onboarding, Provisioning, First Month, Second Month — with employee cards |
| AI Welcome Emails | LLM-personalized welcome emails sent with self-service form links |
| 4-Step Onboarding Wizard | General Info → Job & Assets → Documents → Onboarding Planning |
| AI Onboarding Plans | LLM generates role-specific first-week schedules with calendar invites |
| Asset Provisioning | Auto-assign equipment packages based on role (laptops, monitors, peripherals) |
| Document Management | Upload, track, and manage onboarding documents (NDA, policies, etc.) |
| Employee Verification | Confirm joining, assign company email, employee ID, and activate |

---

### 3. 👤 Employee Portal

**Purpose**: Self-service onboarding experience for new hires.

| Capability | Description |
|---|---|
| Personal Info Form | New hire fills in personal details, emergency contacts, bank info via a secure link |
| Document Access | View and download company policies, NDA, and onboarding documents |
| Onboarding Schedule | See their personalized first-week calendar with sessions, introductions, and training |
| Status Tracking | Real-time visibility into their onboarding progress and pending actions |

---

## End-to-End Pipeline

```
RECRUITER                         HR                              EMPLOYEE
─────────                    ──────────                      ─────────────
Selected Candidates          Waiting for Input                Receives Welcome Email
       │                            │                                │
  AI Generates Offer         Sends Welcome Email              Fills Self-Service Form
       │                            │                                │
  Sends Offer Letter         Reviews Form Response            Views Onboarding Plan
       │                            │                                │
  LLM Classifies Reply       4-Step Onboarding Wizard         Accesses Documents
       │                            │                                │
  Accepted ──────────────►   Provisions Assets + Plan         Joins on Day 1
                                    │                                │
                             Confirms Joined ◄───────────── Reports to Office
                                    │
                                 ACTIVE ✓
```

---

## AI Capabilities (AWS Bedrock / Claude)

| Function | Portal | What It Does |
|---|---|---|
| Offer Letter Generation | Recruiter | Drafts personalized offer letters from candidate context |
| Reply Classification | Recruiter | Classifies candidate email replies into actionable categories |
| Counter-Offer Drafting | Recruiter | Suggests negotiation responses |
| Welcome Email Generation | HR | Writes personalized welcome emails for new hires |
| Onboarding Plan Generation | HR | Creates role-specific first-week schedules |

---

## Impact

| Metric | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| Offer letter turnaround | 2–3 days | **Minutes** (AI-generated) |
| Reply classification | Manual email reading | **Automated** (LLM) |
| Recruiter → HR handoff | Copy-paste across tools | **One-click** transfer |
| Onboarding plan creation | Generic template | **AI-personalized** per role |
| Pipeline visibility | Fragmented | **Single dashboard** per role |
| New hire Day-1 readiness | Inconsistent | **100% provisioned** |
